abstract: >
  ziviDomeLive is a Java library for the Processing platform that streamlines the
  development of real-time visual experiences for fulldome projection, mono VR and
  other immersive installations. It provides multiple projection modes (domemaster,
  equirectangular, cubemap), dynamic resolution switching and Syphon/Spout routing
  for live video output.
